602668735573331968:::Mon May 25 02:53:18 +0000 2015:::That wraps up today's media conference. #myheartbeatstrue:::None
602668685103247360:::Mon May 25 02:53:06 +0000 2015:::Jones says this week will be a good challenge after we had two strong performances against Port Adelaide last year.:::None

column2: our game plan will stack up against them... But we're well aware of how good they are.:::None

column1: 602668234647547906:::Mon May 25 02:51:18 +0000 2015:::Jones says we've had a tough run of injury over the past month... it'll be good to have competition for selection again.:::None
602668115877601280:::Mon May 25 02:50:50 +0000 2015:::Jones: We'll just focus on backing up and if we play our best footy we've got a good chance.:::None
602667995383484416:::Mon May 25 02:50:21 +0000 2015:::Jones: We're not going to underestimate Port Adelaide... we understand the talent they've got and the quality of footy they can play.:::None
602667864944877568:::Mon May 25 02:49:50 +0000 2015:::Jones says we started to get back to 18-man footy yesterday and our confidence grew throughout the match.:::None
602667775891374082:::Mon May 25 02:49:29 +0000 2015:::Jones: I think the gap between our best and worst footy
column2: when we play team footy and when we don't

column1: 602667640637685760:::Mon May 25 02:48:57 +0000 2015:::Jones says some of Daniher's messages were really significant and "something we can take hold of".:::None
602667545288519681:::Mon May 25 02:48:34 +0000 2015:::Jones: (Daniher) spoke about hope and belief... you go through the pain and the anger but at some point you have to stand up and fight.:::None
602667395585474560:::Mon May 25 02:47:58 +0000 2015:::Jones: Daniher's resilience and his fight and his determination to make a difference is really something.:::None
602667310684377089:::Mon May 25 02:47:38 +0000 2015:::Jones: For the boys that didn't understand the situation
column2: to see (Daniher) was quite confronting. But I think his character is so important.:::None

column1: 602667134989139968:::Mon May 25 02:46:56 +0000 2015:::Jones: We got back to having 18-22 contributors on the weekend and it made a big difference.:::None
602667042039205890:::Mon May 25 02:46:34 +0000 2015:::Jones says he's really happy with Hogan's competitiveness and also his ability to play his role on the day.:::None
602666949760458753:::Mon May 25 02:46:12 +0000 2015:::Jones: For a young kid to come in like Hogan has
column2: I haven't seen anything like that... young tall key position players it's tough for them:::None

column1: 602666756218310657:::Mon May 25 02:45:26 +0000 2015:::Jones says we've got "an exciting group":::None
602666713046388737:::Mon May 25 02:45:16 +0000 2015:::Jones: Credit to the group... we've had a real focus on making sure we move on from a loss and not dwelling on it.:::None
602666559266430976:::Mon May 25 02:44:39 +0000 2015:::Jones: We understand we're still a long way off but I think when we play our good footy we're pretty exciting.:::None
602666416685223936:::Mon May 25 02:44:05 +0000 2015:::Jones says we didn't start well yesterday but our confidence grew throughout the game.:::None

column3: the players watched footage of our best games.:::None

column1: 602666228537171968:::Mon May 25 02:43:20 +0000 2015:::Jones: Last week was difficult to swallow at the time... on Sunday we set about preparing for the week and freshening up.:::None
602666070193737729:::Mon May 25 02:42:42 +0000 2015:::Jones: I think the resilience shown by the boys was really impressive... it was great to bounce back.:::None
